  <brief_title>A Study of Capecitabine (Xeloda) in Patients With Metastatic Colorectal Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-label Study of the Safety, Tolerability, and Response Rate of Xeloda in Treatment-na√Øve Patients With Metastatic Colorectal Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
