  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy, safety, and pharmacoeconomics of oral capecitabine in
      patients with metastatic colorectal cancer. The anticipated time on study treatment is 3-12
      months, and the target sample size is 28 individuals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
